deserved the death sentence.

318
00:21:28,987 --> 00:21:32,691
You only learned about the possibility
of him being falsely accused

319
00:21:32,758 --> 00:21:34,493
when Prosecutor Momose visited you.

320
00:21:35,260 --> 00:21:36,161
What do you mean?

321
