There was a video that proved
Mr. Yusaku Shimizu's alibi.

322
00:21:40,966 --> 00:21:43,869
But Prosecutor Datehara covered it up.

323
00:21:44,469 --> 00:21:45,304
Impossible.

324
00:21:45,370 --> 00:21:46,738
Mr. Shimizu…

325
00:21:48,707 --> 00:21:49,641
is innocent.

326
00:21:50,909 --> 00:21:53,312
<i>You were clearly shaken.</i>

327
00:21:53,378 --> 00:21:56,048
<i>That's what was noted in Momose's records.</i>

328
00:21:57,916 --> 00:21:59,618
You realized your error

329
00:22:00,118 --> 00:22:02,354
and have been regretting it
ever since, right?

330
00:22:03,755 --> 00:22:07,759
That's why you've been donating
and volunteering at the children's home

331
00:22:07,826 --> 00:22:09,861
where Saya Shimizu lives.

332
