339
00:22:34,086 --> 00:22:35,520
I don't know anything.

340
00:22:39,257 --> 00:22:40,292
Datehara…

341
00:22:41,159 --> 00:22:45,597
He never tolerates anyone
who strays from his rules.

342
00:22:48,934 --> 00:22:51,503
You'll be crushed soon too.

343
00:22:52,037 --> 00:22:53,004
I don't care.

344
00:22:55,240 --> 00:22:58,810
When you have nothing to lose,
you can do anything.

345
00:23:00,779 --> 00:23:01,813
Am I wrong,

346
