348
00:23:22,834 --> 00:23:23,668
Hey.

349
00:23:23,735 --> 00:23:24,803
Seriously, Yuna!

350
00:23:25,370 --> 00:23:26,204
Welcome back.

351
00:23:27,572 --> 00:23:28,573
