360
00:23:46,658 --> 00:23:49,861
People who break the rules get punished.

361
00:23:51,029 --> 00:23:55,167
And it's your father's job
to administer these punishments.

362
00:23:55,801 --> 00:23:57,135
Forget it.

363
00:23:57,202 --> 00:23:58,403
