00:25:11,643 --> 00:25:13,478
<i>Then I'm fine.</i>

394
00:25:14,179 --> 00:25:15,447
<i>I'll trust you and wait.</i>

395
00:25:18,783 --> 00:25:21,152
<i>We have the media's attention right now.</i>

396
00:25:21,219 --> 00:25:24,990
