it could cause issues for Ms. Saya.

397
00:25:26,825 --> 00:25:28,093
Thank you so much…

398
00:25:29,394 --> 00:25:30,562
for everything.

399
00:25:31,263 --> 00:25:33,265
And for pushing for the retrial.

400
00:25:33,331 --> 00:25:36,301
Thank you for doing your best
despite the lost footage.

401
00:25:37,035 --> 00:25:37,936
Right now,

402
00:25:38,537 --> 00:25:43,108
