It contains his notes from back then.

420
00:27:09,894 --> 00:27:11,296
Did you find any clues?

421
00:27:13,098 --> 00:27:14,265
No.

422
00:27:14,833 --> 00:27:15,934
It's just that…

423
00:27:17,936 --> 00:27:19,638
