424
00:27:23,274 --> 00:27:24,109
May I?

425
00:27:26,244 --> 00:27:27,112
Sure.

426
00:27:40,558 --> 00:27:42,160
<i>Five days since my arrest.</i>

427
00:27:42,227 --> 00:27:43,528
You did it, didn't you?

428
00:27:43,595 --> 00:27:45,230
<i>I was interrogated about my alibi.</i>

429
00:27:45,296 --> 00:27:46,231
Please let me go.

430
