No.

458
00:28:50,562 --> 00:28:52,630
<i>I've lost even the will to respond.</i>

459
00:28:53,364 --> 00:28:57,302
<i>What can I possibly say
to someone who won't listen?</i>

460
00:29:01,139 --> 00:29:03,408
<i>Fifty-two days since my arrest.</i>

461
00:29:03,475 --> 00:29:06,277
How do you think your daughter
will continue living?

